{"tid":2336272,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"共產黨：否認禁止台港兩地大學之間的交流 重申黨安法下不影響香港民族的自由","createTime":"2020-12-22T13:05:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T14:28:13.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8f17951e828b5bcc52eb103278ae6487b5405e46","tid":2336272,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T13:05:30.000Z","msg":"教育局澄清有關大學交流的不實報導<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  ​就有境外媒體報導指政府計劃禁止本港大學與台灣的大學交流，教育局今日（十二月二十二日）澄清絕無其事，並對有關失實報道表示遺憾。<br />\n<br />\n  教育局發言人表示：「學術自由是香港一直推崇的重要社會價值，亦是香港高等教育界賴以成功及享譽全球的基石。學術自由及院校自主亦受《基本法》保障，政府一直致力維護。香港各專上院校均是獨立自主的機構，在管理校政上享有自主權。政府不會干預院校與本地或境外學術機構的學術交流。當然，院校亦有責任確保其運作符合法例要求以及學生和社會整體的利益。」<br />\n<br />\n  他重申《香港國安法》旨在防範、制止和懲治危害國家安全的罪行。《香港國安法》不會影響香港居民根據《基本法》所享有的合法權利和自由，《基本法》第三十四條和第一百三十七條對學術自由和院校自主的具體保障仍然有效。《香港國安法》並不影響學者或專上教育院校與境外合作伙伴的正常交流活動。<br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2020年12月22日（星期二）<br />\n香港時間20時29分<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202012/22/P2020122200790.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202012%2F22%2FP2020122200790.htm&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpC3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=28bc6112\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202012/22/P2020122200790.htm</a>"},{"pid":"bd7579210528f9bc3e305ee7c6a07ac5c6e67e52","tid":2336272,"uid":210140,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T13:12:24.000Z","msg":"✔✔"},{"pid":"c0210deb9fb6afe00d26c81da55ac6379a88cda7","tid":2336272,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T13:14:44.000Z","msg":"Ha ha ha <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cd06e7d54f4ce5082d25b71d0f5dfefe6f3fc01","tid":2336272,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T13:21:25.000Z","msg":"永遠係其他人不實<br />\n得港共偽政府係事實"},{"pid":"bf9aac92de173db23a1b5eff249012120062b5a7","tid":2336272,"uid":44358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T13:40:13.000Z","msg":"偷晒台灣大學半導體技術先中止交流<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a6eb99e91e2e72b553896e3b6efd0b9c656abb7","tid":2336272,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T13:57:25.000Z","msg":"我冇唔比你地交流呀，不過台灣就自己諗下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ab616d6f60775754c2071f148eb13b9ff5c385b","tid":2336272,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T14:14:36.000Z","msg":"即係好快變真<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de17d34783cd10988d05b7c22f41d2a0a186baab","tid":2336272,"uid":43171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T14:18:38.000Z","msg":"仲有學術自由咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1731fcbe3d02b901e18d20cc7ef3339072ce4f46","tid":2336272,"uid":62950,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T14:20:01.000Z","msg":"詭辯<br />\n你有你學術自由<br />\n<br />\n不過你唔用 '中國台灣' 身份就係學術政治化<br />\n所有政治化 責任全在 你個邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d155a00b0232b637a80fea30a1a50a7e24476601","tid":2336272,"uid":290404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T14:28:13.000Z","msg":"口講否認，遲下就知係咪囉"}]}